0 DIFFERENCES~

There are a lot of features different with LoC compared to other muds.
This will go in a brief discussion of the differences and what to expect.

-LoC is known for its high damage, quick level system. That just changed.
We no longer are a exp fast do 900 hp of damage mud. In doing this there
are a lot of changes that need to be done. We have done our best to balance
out everything to what we could. That is why we are doing a playertest. 
This will allow us to test our characters and understand where balancing
issues need to change.

-Evolve, Ascension and Remorting. There are different costs per remort,
type remort cost to check those out. There are also ascend costs, when
your ascend, simply type remort cost again. When you remort, you cannot
just remort in any room. There is a specific place designated on the map
for this. The place is fairly easy to find and the remort, evolve, and
ascension rooms are all in the same area. Once you find there, you have
to type remort remort. Once you remort its a normal transform. You 
can NO LONGER DO AUGMENTS UPON REMORT. You must buy augments now.
There is also a room in the general map for this. To evolve, you must
meet the "ascend cost" requirements. It is the same cost per ascension
as it is for evolving. HELP EVOLVE HELP ASCENSION for more info.

-Map Problems- if you having map problems, typically its because your
browser dosnt support the specifications we have made to it. Try typing
the following commands: noibm, mapspam, nospam

That should allow you to see the map without it loosing its shape.

-Shards, Shards are quite unique, they are extremely rare and hard
to get. There is a massive quest that you must complete in order to 
get a shard. Type HELP SHARD for information on the specific shards.

-Capture, type help capture for more information, but basically you
capture an outpost, that dosn't belong to either good or evil and
once you capture it, it becomes yours. Your alignment enjoys a nice
bonus to attributes until another align can capture it. Help capture
for more info.

-Weapons, we have a lot of different flags now, type help weaponaddons
for more information.

