0 'Align-Elements' Shard Shards~

Many centuries ago there was a great Wizard that could inscribe a rune
on the forehead of the worthy. This rune would give the adventurer
extraordinary powers based on which rune he/she had gotten. There are
four elemental runes, Air, Fire, Earth, Water..Whichever rune the
adventurer picks, their element rune would increase that elements power.
The rune also has magical powers protecting them against certain
elemental attacks. It is not known where this great Wizard is, nor if
he is still alive, but rumors abound of even greater runes which
inflict damage on those of the opposite align.

Here is a brief description of what each element does:
Fire element:  adds approximately 15percent damage to fire spells
               lowers the damage you take from fire spells
